## Limitations

The findings are based on current trends and predictions, which may evolve as new technologies emerge and existing ones are refined. Additionally, the implementation of these technologies will depend on regulatory approvals, healthcare infrastructure, and societal acceptance. The potential cybersecurity risks associated with digital health technologies also pose a significant challenge that needs to be addressed to ensure patient safety and data privacy.